description:
Compare Darwinism with creationism in this riveting, research-based video. In this lecture, Darwinism and natural selection are contrasted with origin by design. Biochemical evolution, speciation, and the origin of variety are presented in full multimedia format. This fascinating lecture includes examples of irreducible complexity, and discusses the core of genetic problems involved in the evolutionary process. The data is presented in simple terms so that everyone can understand the principles involved.
